.TH "slim_stream_prepare" 9 "slim_stream_prepare" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
slim_stream_prepare \- Prepare a SLIMbus Stream
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" slim_stream_prepare
.BI "(struct slim_stream_runtime *rt "  ","
.BI "struct slim_stream_config *cfg "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "rt" 12
instance of slim stream runtime to configure
.IP "cfg" 12
new configuration for the stream
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This API will configure SLIMbus stream with config parameters from cfg.
return zero on success and error code on failure. From ASoC DPCM framework,
this state is linked to \fBhw_params\fP operation.
